     <property name="toolTip">
      <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Timing offset from the lead event to search for the lag event.  An offset of 0.1s might be appropriate for visual stimuli - as the subject has not fully perceived the stimuli yet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This can be negative (helpful if the lead/lag have nearly identical timing)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
     </property>
